cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with 3D hand and human pose estimation from a single depth map using deep learning-based methods.
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the accurate estimation of human pose is important for robotics applications such as human-robot interaction and manipulation.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper proposes a novel approach for 3D pose estimation using a 3D CNN and voxel-to-voxel prediction.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with the use of deep learning-based methods for 3D pose estimation.
- cs.GR (Graphics) is a less likely category as the paper does not focus on graphics or visualization, but rather on the estimation of 3D pose from a single depth map.
